caption: As I reflect on this special day, I feel a deep sense of gratitude for the extraordinary woman who filled my life with love and wisdom. Happy birthday in paradise, beloved Mom. Your boundless affection remains the driving force behind my journey, illuminating my way even from a distance. I hold our cherished moments close to my heart, and your spirit continues to guide me every day. 🌹❤️❤️❤️❤️
